{"tid":1185410,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母香港垃圾地方真係比狗都唔住","createTime":"2019-06-04T09:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T07:47:01.000Z","uid":59684,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3908b369a79f880c3ae32ac1d09254e7cf299a40","tid":1185410,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"落緊雨都可以又熱又局到死，仲要石屎森林，又逼又窄，成日上面滴水，人又多到仆街，有風都吹唔到啦，條路窄唔夠位行，根本成個九龍成寨有時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲蚊最鍾意垃圾地方，搞到成日比蚊咬<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得香港成日有人自殺，返工讀書已經夠辛苦，仲要住啲咁嘅地方，仲要咁既垃圾地方啲樓都可以又貴又細，挪威既監獄仲好過佢<br />\n<br />\n咁既地方邊可以生活得好<br />\n屌好想移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5123d424f468f733fce31107269c03732f84f714","tid":1185410,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"移囉 等咩"},{"pid":"f4dfbe9d2b50eed745cd9123ed3bdce340e68be5","tid":1185410,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"菲律賓"},{"pid":"334af103bc34bd46771fd0a511d952da38a9f13b","tid":1185410,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"好行夾唔送"},{"pid":"6cdb145991dd7baa500f2d65c62f5f131b505ae8","tid":1185410,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5123d424f468f733fce31107269c03732f84f714","tid":1185410,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"移囉 等咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"有＄先得架"},{"pid":"6e417d79ae9d8122c356455bcb4840f03e3bd87d","tid":1185410,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cdb145991dd7baa500f2d65c62f5f131b505ae8","tid":1185410,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5123d424f468f733fce31107269c03732f84f714","tid":1185410,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T